    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disclamer</h2>This game brings a lot of anger due to nearly inadequate challenges and an unbalanced difficulty curve. Most people who tested the game dropped it around level 5. Think twice before purchasing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2>Just Dodge, LOL is a top-down action game that brings a set of trials to the player, while requiring mastering of just one skill: dodging. Earn money, purchase upgrades, and beat challenges to prove that you deserve to be called a Dodge Grandmaster. The game is designed to be hard: no pain - no gain.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Feartures</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">  <li> No lives or game-overs, repeat each trial as long as you want.<br>  </li><li> Multiple upgrades allow for building different completion strategies.<br>  </li><li> Secrets. Secrets everywhere...<br>  </li><li> Various level designs.<br>  </li><li> Catchy soundtrack!</li></ul>",
